Class KodeKsData.KodeKsMove

  • java.lang.Object
    • KodeKsData.KodeKsMove

    Enclosing class:
    KodeKsData

    public static class KodeKsData.KodeKsMove
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A KodeKsMove object represents a move in the game of KodeKs. It holds the row and column of the piece that is to be moved and the row and column of the square to which it is to be moved. (This class makes no guarantee that the move is legal.)
